---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Story — AcaiFlow" description="Superfood. Glow. Vibe. The story behind AcaiFlow — real food that makes you feel good.">
  <section class="bg-berry text-cream-warm">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5 py-24 md:py-32">
      <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-xs opacity-80 mb-5">Our Story</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-[0.95]">
        superfood.<br />glow. vibe.
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 py-20 text-lg leading-relaxed text-coffee space-y-8">
    <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display text-berry leading-snug">
      Eating well should be simple — not stressful. That's why we created AcaiFlow.
    </p>

    <p>
      We believe in real food that makes you feel good — nourishing bowls, wholesome ingredients, and flavours that keep your body and spirit in flow.
      No complicated diets, no calorie anxiety — just clean, balanced meals that fit your daily lifestyle.
    </p>

    <figure class="my-12 -mx-5 md:mx-0 md:rounded-3xl overflow-hidden">
      <img src="/images/PHY_0038.jpg" alt="An acai bowl styled with natural foliage" class="w-full h-auto" loading="lazy" />
    </figure>

    <p>
      Our menu celebrates natural superfoods — from antioxidant-rich acai and tropical fruits to proteins and grains that fuel your day.
      Every bowl, smoothie, and toast is designed to keep you glowing, energized, and balanced from the inside out.
    </p>

    <p>
      We're here to make healthy living effortless. Tasty, fresh, and full of good vibes — that's the AcaiFlow promise.
    </p>

    <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display text-berry leading-snug pt-4">
      Because when you eat well, you flow daily.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-cream border-t border-berry/10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5 py-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl text-coffee">Let's flow together 🌿</h2>
      <a href="/menu" class="inline-flex mt-7 items-center gap-2 bg-raspberry hover:bg-raspberry/90 text-white font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-full transition-colors">
        See what's on the menu
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
